Low-Cost Robot Arm MJCF assets

This directory vendors the Apache-2.0 low-cost robot arm MuJoCo model from
the sibling rlola-eval experiment assets.

The model description identifies the arm as a simplified MJCF of the
Low-Cost Robot Arm originally developed by Alexander Koch and updated by the
HuggingFace LeRobot Team as Kochv1.1. It is derived from the public URDF
description referenced in README.md.

See LICENSE and README.md in this directory for the upstream attribution and
license text.
